OL,3,CTour de France to go through Wales for
OL,4,Cthe first time
OL,6,FThe Tour de France route is to go
OL,7,Fthrough Wales for the first time, it
OL,8,Fhas been announced.
OL,10,FThe Tour de France and Tour de France
OL,11,FFemmes avec Zwift, will both take
OL,12,Fplace in the UK in 2027, with millions
OL,13,Fexpected to line the streets. It will
OL,14,Fbe the first ever staging of the Tour
OL,15,Fde France Femmes avec Zwift in the UK.
OL,17,FThe men's Tour will begin in
OL,18,FEdinburgh. The actual route for Wales
OL,19,Fwon't be confirmed until later in the
OL,20,Fyear.
