OL,3,CTour de France to go through Wales for
OL,4,Cthe first time
OL,6,FIt will be the third time that the
OL,7,Fopening stage of the Tour has been
OL,8,Fheld in the UK, the last time being
OL,9,F2014 where it began in Leeds with
OL,10,Ffurther stages finishing in Sheffield
OL,11,Fand London.
OL,13,FIt will be the first time the event
OL,14,Fhas been held in Wales, with last
OL,15,Fyear's Grand Depart taking place in
OL,16,FFlorence, Italy, and the 2026 race due
OL,17,Fto start in Barcelona.
