OL,6,FA social impact programme is also set
OL,7,Fto be delivered as part of the build-
OL,8,Fup to the 2027 Tour de France and Tour
OL,9,Fde France Femmes avec Zwift Grand
OL,10,FDeparts.
OL,12,FBritish Cycling says it "will deliver
OL,13,Flong-lasting benefits for thousands of
OL,14,Fpeople across the country by tackling
OL,15,Finactivity, improving mental
OL,16,Fwellbeing, boosting economic growth
OL,17,Fand supporting communities to thrive."
