OL,3,CTour de France to go through Wales for
OL,4,Cthe first time
OL,6,FFirst Minister of Wales, Eluned
OL,7,FMorgan, said: "The Welsh stage of the
OL,8,F2027 UK Grand Depart promises to be a
OL,9,Fmemorable experience for competitors
OL,10,Fand fans alike. Boasting stunning
OL,11,Flandscapes, warm and welcoming
OL,13,Fcommunities and an ever-growing
OL,14,Ffanbase of cycling enthusiasts, Wales
OL,15,Fwill provide the ultimate challenge
OL,16,Fand a unique Welsh 'Croeso' for the
OL,17,Fworld's biggest cycle race.
