OL,3,CTour de France to go through Wales for
OL,4,Cthe first time
OL,6,F"We will build on our successful track
OL,7,Frecord of hosting road cycling events,
OL,8,Fensuring the Tour De France has a
OL,9,Fpositive and lasting impact on cycling
OL,10,Fin Wales, by showcasing Wales as a top
OL,11,Finternational destination for cyclists
OL,12,Fand encouraging more people in Wales
OL,13,Fto get into cycling."
OL,15,FWales in the Tour de France
OL,17,FIn 2018, cyclist Geraint Thomas MBE
OL,18,Fbecame the first Welshman to win the
OL,19,FTour de France, and only the third
OL,20,FBritish rider after Bradley Wiggins
OL,21,Fand Chris Froome.
