OL,3,CTour de France to go through Wales for
OL,4,Cthe first time
OL,6,FHis victory came 50 years after the
OL,7,Ffirst appearance by a Welsh cyclist in
OL,8,Fthe famous race.
OL,10,FColin Lewis, who rode in the 1964
OL,11,FOlympic Games, was the first Welshman
OL,12,Fto compete in the Tour de France in
OL,13,F1968 as part of a 10-strong British
OL,14,Fteam.
OL,16,FThe Tour de France Femmes, and
OL,17,Fprevious incarnations held under
OL,18,Fdifferent names, have seen the likes
OL,19,Fof Welsh rider Nicole Cooke ride into
OL,20,Fthe cycling history books with a win
OL,21,Fin the 2006 Grande Boucle.
